Author: scrapthat1986
Text: This is it! Thank you for taking the time to write this. They are probably happy to see me healthy-ish so they don’t say anything at all. Made me think that maybe I “need” some reaction for me to send me into starving mode. I hate living like this.

Author: Shorse_rider
Text: They have tried to push you before and it clearly hasn't worked. So they probably see no point in those things because they consider it ineffective and perhaps insensitive. None of these people are qualified in communicating with someone who has an eating disorder.
